Zappacosta: &ldquo;When I saw Andreas on the ground I figured I could come on, as the Coach already tested Azpi as a CB during the week. I trained hard and tried to ensure I was always ready, as I couldn't stand the thought of a chance like this coming along and I wouldn't be prepared&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;We're happy to make the Final. Playing every 3 days, we don't have time to practice the tactics or movements. Those little details are so important, especially when you play in a defensive line, and it requires constant work to ensure you're all on the same page.&quot;

